wikipedia_page.main: Harry Yates (26 September 1925 – 26 November 1987) was a professional footballer who played as an inside forward for Huddersfield Town, Darlington, Headington United, Bedford Town and Nuneaton Borough.He was born in Huddersfield in 1925 and died in Liverpool in 1987 at the age of 62.
